{
  "script_id": "game-of-life",
  "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiNeural",
  "voice_key": "yunxi",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "game-of-life",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-of-life/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.73,
      "size": 43632,
      "text": "欢迎来到康威生命游戏。它不是真正的游戏，而是一个奇妙的数学世界。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-of-life",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-of-life/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.99,
      "size": 47808,
      "text": "1970年，数学家约翰·康威设计了它。整个世界只是一张布满方格的网格。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-of-life",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-of-life/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.26,
      "size": 36144,
      "text": "每个格子代表一个细胞，它只有两种状态：活着，或者死去。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-of-life",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-4",
      "filename": "intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-of-life/intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.64,
      "size": 42192,
      "text": "神奇的是，仅靠两条极简单的规则，就能涌现出令人惊叹的复杂图案。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-of-life",
      "section_id": "rules",
      "line_id": "rules-1",
      "filename": "rules-rules-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-of-life/rules-rules-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.5,
      "size": 40032,
      "text": "每个细胞周围有八个邻居。规则只看这八个邻居里有几个是活的。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-of-life",
      "section_id": "rules",
      "line_id": "rules-2",
      "filename": "rules-rules-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-of-life/rules-rules-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.62,
      "size": 41904,
      "text": "第一条规则：如果一个活细胞周围有两个或三个活邻居，它就继续存活。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-of-life",
      "section_id": "rules",
      "line_id": "rules-3",
      "filename": "rules-rules-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-of-life/rules-rules-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.69,
      "size": 43056,
      "text": "邻居太少会孤独而死，邻居太多会拥挤而死。这就是生存的平衡。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-of-life",
      "section_id": "rules",
      "line_id": "rules-4",
      "filename": "rules-rules-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-of-life/rules-rules-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.37,
      "size": 37872,
      "text": "第二条规则：如果一个死细胞周围恰好有三个活邻居，它就会诞生。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-of-life",
      "section_id": "rules",
      "line_id": "rules-5",
      "filename": "rules-rules-5.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-of-life/rules-rules-5.mp3",
      "duration": 2.8,
      "size": 44784,
      "text": "这套规则被称为 B3/S23。所有细胞同时根据它更新，进入下一代。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-of-life",
      "section_id": "patterns",
      "line_id": "pat-1",
      "filename": "patterns-pat-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-of-life/patterns-pat-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.82,
      "size": 45072,
      "text": "最有名的图案是滑翔机。五个细胞组成的小队，竟然能在网格上斜向爬行。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-of-life",
      "section_id": "patterns",
      "line_id": "pat-2",
      "filename": "patterns-pat-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-of-life/patterns-pat-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.09,
      "size": 33408,
      "text": "每过四代，滑翔机就完整地向前移动一格，永不停歇。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-of-life",
      "section_id": "patterns",
      "line_id": "pat-3",
      "filename": "patterns-pat-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-of-life/patterns-pat-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32256,
      "text": "闪烁灯是最简单的振荡器，三个细胞不停地横竖切换。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-of-life",
      "section_id": "patterns",
      "line_id": "pat-4",
      "filename": "patterns-pat-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-of-life/patterns-pat-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.43,
      "size": 38880,
      "text": "脉冲星则壮观得多，它是一个周期为三的巨大振荡结构，像心脏一样搏动。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-of-life",
      "section_id": "patterns",
      "line_id": "pat-5",
      "filename": "patterns-pat-5.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-of-life/patterns-pat-5.mp3",
      "duration": 2.4,
      "size": 38448,
      "text": "高斯帕滑翔机枪更不可思议，它会源源不断地发射出新的滑翔机。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-of-life",
      "section_id": "emergence",
      "line_id": "emg-1",
      "filename": "emergence-emg-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-of-life/emergence-emg-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.49,
      "size": 39888,
      "text": "这就是数学中\"涌现\"的概念：复杂的整体行为，源自简单的局部规则。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-of-life",
      "section_id": "emergence",
      "line_id": "emg-2",
      "filename": "emergence-emg-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-of-life/emergence-emg-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.12,
      "size": 33840,
      "text": "没有谁在指挥这些细胞，它们只是各自遵守同一条规则。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-of-life",
      "section_id": "emergence",
      "line_id": "emg-3",
      "filename": "emergence-emg-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-of-life/emergence-emg-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.47,
      "size": 39456,
      "text": "生命游戏被证明是图灵完备的，理论上它能完成任何计算机能做的计算。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-of-life",
      "section_id": "emergence",
      "line_id": "emg-4",
      "filename": "emergence-emg-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-of-life/emergence-emg-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.39,
      "size": 38304,
      "text": "从蚁群到大脑，从星系到生命本身，自然界处处都是这种涌现现象。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-of-life",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-of-life/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.23,
      "size": 35712,
      "text": "现在轮到你了。点击网格上的格子，亲手创造你的初始生命。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-of-life",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-of-life/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.25,
      "size": 36000,
      "text": "点击\"随机\"按钮，看看混沌的初始状态会演化出怎样的结局。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-of-life",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-3",
      "filename": "interaction-int-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-of-life/interaction-int-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32256,
      "text": "调整速度滑块，放慢节奏，仔细观察每一代的变化。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-of-life",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-of-life/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.26,
      "size": 36144,
      "text": "我们认识了生命游戏：一个由 B3/S23 规则驱动的元胞自动机。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-of-life",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-of-life/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.36,
      "size": 37728,
      "text": "我们见证了滑翔机的爬行、脉冲星的搏动，以及简单规则的无穷可能。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-of-life",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-of-life/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.82,
      "size": 45072,
      "text": "数学之美，正在于这种从简单到复杂的奇妙跨越。继续探索吧！"
    }
  ],
